metadata.name: Blackbird Love
metadata.description:
Blackbird Love gotta hold on me.
Blackbird Love won’t let me be.

Blackbird Love you’re all I know.
Blackbird Love where did you go?

Blackbird Love where can you be?
Blackbird Love come back to me. 






Artwork:
11” x 15” Oil on 140 lb. Paper

Audio:
Vocals, Harmonica & Percussion: LBJ
Sound Engineer/Producer: Graham Wade @Gramshack
